====== H4374: מְכַסֶּה ======

===== Source =====

from  H3680 ;

===== Meaning =====

a  covering , i.e.  garment ; specifically, a  coverlet  (for a bed), an  awning  (from the sun); also the  omentum  (as covering the intestines)

===== Definitions =====

  - covering
  - garment
  - coverlet
  - awning
  - omentum

===== Usage =====

clothing, to cover, that which covereth.
